ISLAMABAD, Aug 05 (APP): Minister for Information and Broadcasting Chaudhry Fawad Hussain said on Thursday that the government, in respect of Ashura e Muharram ul Haram, has postponed the events planned to present its three-year performance.
In a statement he said that these events were scheduled to be held on August 18 but now have been deferred for a week.
